            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E7%A7%B0%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E8%82%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E6%88%96%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E7%A7%B0%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E8%82%BA%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E6%88%96%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医生称部分肺结节或自动消失#</span></a>】肺结节主要分为实性结节和亚实性结节（磨玻璃结节），四川大学华西医院肺癌中心专家团队解释，大部分肺结节都是良性的且不会“癌变”，部分炎性病变引起的肺结节可能会自动消失👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（四川大学华西医院）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4970930594840596" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">四川观察的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/beebff5fly1hk40n8gh9mj20u01404dr.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Ok58WFCelx08anebjiOI01041200dUWC0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700742940&amp;ssig=CAPXgM4LS9&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/wzQY666ulx08aneaIsA0010412008ajb0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700742940&amp;ssig=%2F%2Fv4BVxK7Y&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ohyNitMRlx08anebgHMQ010412004hDL0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700742940&amp;ssig=VrD4%2FPS5%2Fa&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4970930594840596" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
